column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, n.distance, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, sp.velDisp, pz.z as photoz FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = n.objid JOIN SpecObjAll AS sp on sp.specObjID = n.objid WHERE s.class = GALAXY
